is very expensive.

00:03:20.760 --> 00:03:25.840
People used to use AVIDs
almost exclusively,

00:03:25.840 --> 00:03:31.760
and they set up their whole
workflow based on the film model.

00:03:32.500 --> 00:03:37.030
