00:18:56.520 --> 00:19:00.480
They also were able to go out
to their 23-inch cinema display,

00:19:00.550 --> 00:19:03.110
which was quite nice, high resolution.

00:19:03.490 --> 00:19:07.610
And the look is far better than
what people traditionally have

00:19:07.610 --> 00:19:10.430
worked with in an offline situation.

00:19:10.450 --> 00:19:14.660
Traditionally,
offline media looks very blocky,

00:19:14.660 --> 00:19:15.910
very low res.

00:19:15.910 --> 00:19:17.740
This was far better.

00:19:17.740 --> 00:19:19.500
They could see focus.

00:19:19.800 --> 00:19:22.970
They had very good color saturation.

00:19:24.130 --> 00:19:28.280
So, with that particular project,
