00:20:13.520 --> 00:20:17.050
And so when we go into
digitize as high definition,

00:20:17.060 --> 00:20:19.880
we're only capturing
the stuff that we need.

00:20:20.050 --> 00:20:24.440
The timecode of that media was
exactly as it was on the HD tapes.

00:20:24.580 --> 00:20:29.750
So Final Cut, we edited this on a
