00:20:29.750 --> 00:20:32.420
card at 10 bit uncompressed.

00:20:32.580 --> 00:20:37.270
So it would take in from the D5s
exactly the clips that it needed.

00:20:37.610 --> 00:20:42.200
It then also took in
all of the transitions,

00:20:42.360 --> 00:20:50.460
filters, color effects, speed changes,
