00:22:48.070 --> 00:22:51.980
that you would run in parallel
and watch on two screens to

00:22:51.980 --> 00:22:54.100
see if everything matched up.

00:22:54.110 --> 00:22:59.440
This was nice because it let us go in
and we could see on the edit machine

00:22:59.440 --> 00:23:03.080
right away if we had any problems.

